_sText:
Fy_grasscity is a small novelty map by me dedicated to a friend. Whether you judge this map on looks, gameplay, or just down right the content in it, i don't care, i made this map for fun. fy_grasscity supports 16 players. Thanks for downloading and playing.

Map includes custom marijuana-related textures and music including:

Cypress Hill - Hits From The Bong
Sublime - Smoke 2 Joints
Rebelution - Green To Black
